snippet.title: Bhide ने किया Jetha पर Ball से वार | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

In this episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah, Bhide and Jethalal select their teams for Gokuldham Premier League (GPL). All the society members start preparing for the match. It is also decided that the losing captain will clean the society with the help of a broom. 

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 176
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the fun episodes of TMKOC - Revisit The Journey: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cSkLfD49YxG8YsjmWdKNU0r

Bhide ने किया Jetha पर Ball से वार | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 46 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 18th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

The hill is on fire, dear son,
And my heart bursts into flames

The hill is on fire, dear son,
And my heart bursts into flames

Pick up the drum and beat up a tempo
I shall sing out my heart that reels in sorrow

I shall sing out my heart that reels in sorrow

The ones who lived shrivelled and shrunken
The ones who huddled in hardship
The ones who have known famine and hunger
They are an army, yet are fearful

Wounds aplenty, dear son
Would speaking of it make them heal?

Would they heal?
Would they heal?
Would they heal, my dear son?

snippet.title: Kya Loge Tum | Akshay Kumar | Amyra Dastur | BPraak | Jaani | Arvindr Khaira | Zohrajabeen
snippet.description:
Desi Melodies presents in association with Cape Of Good Films & Azeem Dayani the first single, 'Kya Loge Tum,' from B Praak's highly anticipated debut album, "Zohrajabeen." The star-studded team of B Praak, Jaani, Arvindr Khaira, and Akshay Kumar reunites for the first time since the pop-culture-defining songs 'Filhall' and 'Filhaal 2.'

The emotionally charged lyrics written by Jaani, along with his heart-wrenching composition, add an extra layer of depth to the already powerful track produced by B Praak himself. Arvindr Khaira takes it to the next level with his visionary direction, featuring Akshay Kumar and Amyra Dastur's palpable chemistry that will leave you wanting more.

Listen to 'Kya Loge Tum' - https://bit.ly/KyaLogeTum

snippet.title: Sushma Andhare | बीडमध्ये महाप्रबोधन यात्रे अगोदर राडा, सुषमा अंधारे - अप्पासाहेब जाधवांमध्ये वाद
snippet.description:
Even before the meeting of the Mahaprabodhan Yatra, there has been a row between Shiv Sainiks of the Thackeray group in Beed. While inspecting the meeting place in the Mane Complex area of ​​Beed city, it was seen that the Shiv Sainiks had clashed. Thackeray's district chief's car has been vandalized.

महाप्रबोधन यात्रेच्या सभेआधीच बीडमध्ये ठाकरे गटाच्या शिवसैनिकांमध्ये राडा झाला आहे. बीड शहराच्या माने कॉम्प्लेक्स परिसरामध्ये सभेच्या ठिकाणची पाहणी करतानाच शिवसैनिकांमध्ये जुंपल्याचं पाहायला मिळालं. ठाकरेंच्या जिल्हाप्रमुखाची गाडी फोडण्याचा प्रकार घडला आहे.

#sushmaandhare #mahaprabodhanyatra #appasahebjadhav #shivsena #beed #marathinews18 #news18lokmat #maharashtranews18 #marathibatmyanews18

snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 45 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 45 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 17th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma

Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra

Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 47 Teaser - 18th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 47 Teaser - 18th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: Phir Aur Kya Chahiye| Zara Hatke Zara Bachke| Vicky K, Sara Ali K, Arijit Singh,Sachin-Jigar,Amitabh
snippet.description:
Lose yourself in the magic of love with the much-awaited song "Phir Aur Kya Chahiye'' from the film 'Zara Hatke Zara Bachke'. Mesmerizing vocals of Arijit Singh perfectly complement the intense chemistry between Sara Ali Khan and Vicky Kaushal. The music is composed by the talented duo Sachin-Jigar, and is here to make your heart skip a beat!

The soulful lyrics penned by Amitabh Bhattacharya will make you feel the love. A must watch movie directed by Laxman Utekar, featuring Sara Ali Khan and Vicky Kaushal.

snippet.description:
The tenth studio recorded single, written, sung and composed by #AnuvJain is here!

Antariksh out now on all streaming platforms : https://anuvjain.lnk.to/Antariksh

For inquiries - anuvjain.work@gmail.com
Instagram - @anuvjain
Manager- aayushman@representmgmt.in

MUSIC PRODUCTION: Angad Singh Bahra & Somanshu Agarwal
DIRECTOR: Maan Boruah
ASST. DIRECTOR: Paras Kumar
CREATIVE PRODUCER: Maan Boruah, Paras Kumar

2ND DOP: Karan

GAFFER: Jai Singh
ART DIRECTOR: Vikas Kumar

TECH PARTNER: Mount Everest Media
POST PRODUCTION: The Last Slice Studios
VFX ARTIST: Sushant 
SPOT: Sarvar, Karan, Vishwajeet
MAKEUP: Khyati Nagi, Kiran
BTS: Rishita Sharma
CAST COORDINATORS: Rea Kwatra, Shivansh Anand
SUPPORTING CAST: Tanu Awasthy, Shubhangi Bhadani, Niharika Arora, Pavani Jain, Kiyomi, Jiya, Panchoy Baruah, Namrata Singha, Bornali kramsapi , Priyanka Roy, Stanzin Kunsal, Maisha Bagchi, Mishti Raghuvanshi, Samaira Malik, Neeranjana Tiwari, Aalya Malik, Nipun Thapliyal
STYLING: Robertson lyngdoh 
STYLING ASSISTANT: Prerna Sharma 
DRESS DADA: Nishank Kumar 
CLOTHES: @Garuda_SS
JEWELRY: @dashia.in

Antariksh Lyrics

Para 1

Karta mein baatein meri 
Aaine se dekho teri
Tujhse kaise 
Khul ke waise
Bolun mein yeh raaz dil ke?

Ab tere samne hoon 
Kitna kuch mein kehna chahoon
Mujhko yeh bata de fir kyun
Khojun mein alfaaz milke?

Dekho yeh aaina 
Aye na tu kyun yahan?
Aaine mein saath mere
Teri hi toh hai jagah

Uljha hoon alfazon mein hi 
Nikle na awazon mein ki 
Pass mere 
Pass mein aaja
Aa ja na  

Chorus 

Aa re aa x 8

Para 2

Tere sitaron mein yaan 
Ik tara hazaron mein kya?
Mere inn sawalon ka main
Dhundun yoon jawab aise

Lakhon hazaron mein kya?
Mamuli kirdaro mein yaan
Aau inn khayalon mein main 
Banke kuch nayab aise

Tu hi hai aasmaan
Mere dil ko azmaan
Aasmaani taaron mein main
Dhundhu yoon apni jagah

Mere bhi khayalon mein tu
Duniya ke kinaro se yoon 
Pass mere 
Pass mein aaja
Aa ja na  

Chorus

Aa re aa x 8

Bridge

Sun toh

Ek din yeh dil mera 
Hoga benaqaab haan 
Aur phir tujhe nazar ayega 
Ki

Antariksh ki tarah 
Yeh hai behisaab sa
Aur sab tera yeh
ho jayega 
Hi

Para 3

Dil ke afsane mere 
Keh na paya saloon se main
Sochoon yeh khazane mere 
Bantoon sare aaj tujhse 

Bante bahane mere
Taloon kyun na jane kal pe?
Hoon jo ab main pass tere
Betha hoon naraaz khudse

Band hain taalon mein
Taloon sari baatein yeh
Taloon sari baatein kya mein 
Tere intezaar mein?

Rehta hoon umeedon mein kya?
Tu hi mujhko keh degi aa
Pass mere 
Pass mein aaja
Aa ja na  

Chorus

Aa re aa x 8

snippet.title: 5 Proven Ways to Reduce Body Heat (Pigmentation, Rashes, Grey Hair, Body odour, Sweating)

If you can’t stand heat, you feel thirsty all the time, you experience a lot of sweat, overbleeding, hair fall, greying of hair, acidity, skin pigmentation, pimples and anger bothers you then note that this is an indicator that you have excess heat in the body. snippet.description:

In this video, Abhi and Niyu explain how Pakistani army and military controls various aspects of Pakistan. 

#pakistaneconomy #indvspak #abhiandniyu 

Welcome to our YouTube channel, where we delve into pressing global issues. In this video, we explore the economic crisis currently plaguing Pakistan, examining its causes, impacts, and potential solutions.

Pakistan, a country with a rich cultural heritage and immense potential, has been grappling with economic challenges in recent years. Understanding the complexities of this crisis is crucial to formulating effective strategies for recovery and sustainable development.

In this video, we provide a comprehensive analysis of the causes behind the Pakistani economic crisis. Factors such as a growing population, inadequate infrastructure, political instability, corruption, and a high fiscal deficit have all contributed to the country's economic woes. We delve into each of these elements to offer you a deeper understanding of their impact on Pakistan's economy.

Moreover, we shed light on the far-reaching consequences of the economic crisis on various sectors and the lives of ordinary Pakistanis. Rising inflation, unemployment, poverty, and an increasing debt burden have put immense strain on the population, exacerbating social and economic inequalities. By exploring these effects, we aim to highlight the urgency of finding sustainable solutions.

Our video doesn't stop at identifying the challenges; we also explore potential solutions to address the Pakistani economic crisis. From implementing structural reforms to promoting investment and entrepreneurship, we discuss strategies that could revitalize the economy and pave the way for long-term growth and stability.

Join us as we navigate through the intricacies of the Pakistani economic crisis and empower ourselves with knowledge about this critical issue. By understanding the root causes, impacts, and potential solutions, we can collectively contribute to the ongoing discussions and efforts aimed at overcoming this crisis.

Don't forget to like, comment, and share this video to spread awareness about the Pakistani economic crisis and the importance of finding sustainable solutions. Subscribe to our channel for more thought-provoking content on global issues. Together, let's explore and work towards a brighter future for Pakistan and its people.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3774 - 18 May 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3774: Kuch Pao Aur Kuch Kho
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal gets engrossed in his thoughts after Vinu Kaka tells him to change his name in order to get married. Madhavi and Bhide discuss Popatlal's decision about alternating his names. Popatlal discusses the same with his boss, and he suggests Popatlal not change his name. Popatlal decides to ask Jetha about this. So he visits Gada Electronics. Meanwhile, Nattu Kaka and Bagha get excited due to the massive sales. While Jetha is at his godown, he gets a call from Bagha that someone special from Gokhuldham has come to meet him. Jetha gets excited thinking about Babita. Stay tuned! 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3774, 18 May 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: EXTRACTION 2 | Official Hindi Trailer | Netflix India
snippet.description:
Taiyaar ho jaiye apne jeevan ki sabse romanchak safar ke liye! EXTRACTION 2 mein dekhiye Chris Hemsworth ko Tyler Rake ke avtaar main - Netflix par, 16 June.

Hemsworth reunites with director Sam Hargrave, with Joe and Anthony Russo's AGBO producing and Joe Russo writing. Golshifteh Farahani reprises her role from the first film, with Daniel Bernhardt and Tinatin Dalakishvili also co-starring.

This is a sequel to the first film that was based on the graphic novel 'Ciudad' by Ande Parks, from a story by Ande Parks, Joe Russo & Anthony Russo, with illustrations by Fernando León González. EXTRACTION 2 is produced by Anthony Russo, Joe Russo, Mike Larocca, Chris Hemsworth, Patrick Newall and Sam Hargrave, with Angela Russo-Otstot, Jake Aust, Benjamin Grayson, Steven Scavelli, Christopher Markus and Stephen McFeely as executive producers.

Watch EXTRACTION now, only on Netflix.

Taiyaar ho jaiye apne jeevan ki sabse romanchak safar ke liye! EXTRACTION 2 mein dekhiye Chris Hemsworth ko Tyler Rake ke avtaar main - Netflix par, 16 June.

Hemsworth reunites with director Sam Hargrave, with Joe and Anthony Russo's AGBO producing and Joe Russo writing. Golshifteh Farahani reprises her role from the first film, with Daniel Bernhardt and Tinatin Dalakishvili also co-starring.

This is a sequel to the first film that was based on the graphic novel 'Ciudad' by Ande Parks, from a story by Ande Parks, Joe Russo & Anthony Russo, with illustrations by Fernando León González. EXTRACTION 2 is produced by Anthony Russo, Joe Russo, Mike Larocca, Chris Hemsworth, Patrick Newall and Sam Hargrave, with Angela Russo-Otstot, Jake Aust, Benjamin Grayson, Steven Scavelli, Christopher Markus and Stephen McFeely as executive producers.

Watch EXTRACTION now, only on Netflix.

*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

snippet.title: Itihaser Khonje | ইতিহাসের খোঁজে | Thakurmar Jhuli | ঠাকুমার ঝুলি
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to SONY AATH Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBz9qbqujcjIavFmBJW2oZw?sub_confirmation=1

পুরোনো দিনের ইতিহাস জানার আগ্রহে একটি ছেলে বাড়ি থেকে বেরিয়ে পড়লো। অনেক পথ পেরিয়ে সে উপস্থিত হলো এক বড় পাহাড়ের সামনে। গ্রামের লোকের কাছে এই পাহাড়ের নাম শুনে সে বুঝলো এখানেও লুকিয়ে রাখা আছে সম্রাট অশোকের গুপ্তধন। পাহাড়ের গুহার ভিতর ঢুকে সে একটি দরজায় দেখতে পেলো এক অজানা ভাষায় লেখা আছে কিছু। তবে এই লেখা কি গুপ্তধন রাখা স্থানে পৌঁছনোর কোনো ধাঁধাঁ? ছেলেটি কি উদ্ধার করতে পারবে সম্রাট অশোকের গুপ্তধন?
 
A boy came out of the house eager to know the history of old days. After passing a long way, he appeared in front of a big mountain. Hearing the name of this hill from the village people, he understood that the treasure of Emperor Ashoka was hidden here. Entering the mountain cave, he saw something written in an unknown language on a door. But is this writing a puzzle to reach the place where the treasure is kept? Can the boy recover the treasure of Emperor Ashoka?

#sonyaath #ThakurmarJhuli #SonyAath #ঠাকুমারঝুলি #BengaliFairyTales #RupkotharGolpo #comedystory 

About Thakurmar Jhuli:
--------------------------------------
An anthology of Bengali folktales narrated by Thakuma reflects the Indian culture with an insightful moral and holds valuable life lessons.

Click here to watch more:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL5O3zv2ZcASiY-3KOK47cRxhi7M91PTfq

snippet.title: Calcutta High Court: ক্ষমতাসীন ব্যক্তিদের প্রশ্রয় ছাড়া এত কোটি কোটির দুর্নীতি সম্ভব না: অমৃতা সিন্হা
snippet.description:
Calcutta High Court:  অভিষেক-কুন্তলকে ৫০ লক্ষ টাকা জরিমানা করে কড়া পর্যবেক্ষণ বিচারপতি অমৃতা সিন্হার।  'তদন্তে বাধা ও অফিসারদের সন্ত্রস্ত করার উদ্দেশ্যেই রায় পুনর্বিবেচনার আবেদন'। 'বিচারপতি গঙ্গোপাধ্যায় তদন্তকারীদের হয়রানি থেকে রক্ষার জন্যই এমন নির্দেশ দিয়েছিলেন'। 'অপরাধীদের আড়াল করতেই তদন্ত প্রক্রিয়ায় বিলম্ব করানো হয়েছে'। শুরুতেই এই কৌশল কড়া হাতে দমন করতে হবে'। 'দমন না করলে ভবিষ্যতেও একই কৌশলে অন্যান্য তদন্ত একই কারণে বিঘ্নিত হতে পারে'। 'ভবিষ্যতে যাতে আর কেউ এহেন চেষ্টা না করে সেই জন্যই দৃষ্টান্তমূলক আর্থিক জরিমানা করা হয়েছে'। 'অভিষেক বন্দ্যোপাধ্যায়ের তদন্তে সহযোগিতার ক্ষেত্রে লজ্জিত হওয়ার কোনও কারণ থাকা উচিত নয়'। 'অভিষেক বন্দ্যোপাধ্য়ায় দাঁত-নখ বের করে তদন্তের বিরোধিতা করার চেষ্টা করে যাচ্ছেন'। 'তদন্ত থেকে না পালিয়ে তাঁর উচিত তদন্তের মুখোমুখি হয়ে স্বচ্ছতার সঙ্গে বেরিয়ে আসা'। অভিষেক-কুন্তলকে জরিমানার নির্দেশনামায় উল্লেখ বিচারপতি অমৃতা সিন্হার।

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

snippet.title: FAST X | Final Trailer
snippet.description:
The end of the road begins Friday. Watch the FINAL TRAILER Now. #FASTX 

Get tickets now: https://tickets.fastxmovie.com/

The end of the road begins. 

Fast X, the tenth film in the Fast & Furious Saga, launches the final chapters of one of cinema’s most storied and popular global franchises, now in its third decade and still going strong with the same core cast and characters as when it began.

Over many missions and against impossible odds, Dom Toretto (Vin Diesel) and his family have outsmarted, out-nerved and outdriven every foe in their path. Now, they confront the most lethal opponent they’ve ever faced: A terrifying threat emerging from the shadows of the past who’s fueled by blood revenge, and who is determined to shatter this family and destroy everything—and everyone—that Dom loves, forever.  
 
In 2011’s Fast Five, Dom and his crew took out nefarious Brazilian drug kingpin Hernan Reyes and decapitated his empire on a bridge in Rio De Janeiro. What they didn’t know was that Reyes’ son, Dante (Aquaman’s Jason Momoa), witnessed it all and has spent the last 12 years masterminding a plan to make Dom pay the ultimate price. 
 
Dante’s plot will scatter Dom’s family from Los Angeles to the catacombs of Rome, from Brazil to London and from Portugal to Antarctica. New allies will be forged and old enemies will resurface. But everything changes when Dom discovers that his own 8-year-old son (Leo Abelo Perry, Black-ish) is the ultimate target of Dante’s vengeance. 
 
Directed by Louis Leterrier (Clash of the Titans, The Incredible Hulk), Fast X stars returning cast members Michelle Rodriguez, Tyrese Gibson, Chris “Ludacris” Bridges, Nathalie Emmanuel, Jordana Brewster, Sung Kang, Jason Statham, John Cena and Scott Eastwood, with Oscar® winner Helen Mirren and Oscar® winner Charlize Theron. 
 
The film also features an extraordinary new cast including Oscar® winner Brie Larson as Tess, a rogue representative from the Agency; Alan Richtson (Reacher) as Aimes, the new head of the Agency who doesn’t hold the same fondness for Dom’s crew as his predecessor, Mr. Nobody; Daniela Melchior (The Suicide Squad) as a Brazilian street racer with a powerful tie to Dom’s past; and legendary Oscar® winner Rita Moreno as Dom and Mia’s Abuelita Toretto. 
 
Fast X is produced by Neal H. Moritz, Vin Diesel, Justin Lin, Jeff Kirschenbaum and Samantha Vincent. The executive producers are Joseph M. Caracciolo, Jr., David Cain, Chris Morgan, Amanda Lewis and Mark Bomback. www.thefastsaga.com

Official Website: https://www.fastxmovie.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TheFastSaga
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/TheFastSaga
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TheFastSaga
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@thefastsaga

snippet.description:
All the members of the society were struggling for water in the society, everyone is waiting for the tanker to arrive. Meanwhile, Goli comes home smeared with mud. There seems no way out. Stay tuned!


Show Name : Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast: Kush Shah, Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode No: 2756
Produced By: Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 

Click here  to Subscribe to the LIV Comedy channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpEhnqL0y41EpW2TvWAHD7Q?sub_confirmation=1

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Watch the specially curated series of "Haste Raho Comedy":

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3774 - Popatlal Seeks Jethalal's Advice?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

FULL VIDEO | RadhaKrishn Raasleela Part - 545 | Radha Aur Baal Ganesh Ki Bhent #starbharat 

►*About*
-------------

RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

#radhakrishna #sumallika #mallikasingh #radha

snippet.title: MC STΔN  X @KSHMRmusic    HAATH VARTHI  (Official Video) | 2023
snippet.description:
“ HAATH VARTHI “ OUT NOW 🔥💯👇🏼 ( Official Music video ) ✅

STAN FAMILY 🙏🏻 Haq se love uh BHAILOG Bhot pyaarr Sabko
Kattar #fam Phele ki Public Abhi ki Public Sabku Salam bhaiiiiiiiiiii.............🙏🏼

10 Months Bad Gana Aaya 🥺  Baap re Full lambi Hogayeli Maam , i know Broskii Full Kantaal Aata Litreally Mein khud Mere Gaano Ka wait Karta 🥲 Kya bolu Maa ider Bhalta vishay chalu hai Samaj ke lo Baki kuch Nai Tracks on the way …… 🏃🏽

Line Se Appa vishay Khol 💯

Show sum love Gang !! Stay connected 🤝

Performed by: MC Stan, KSHMR
Lyrics: MC Stan
Produced by: KSHMR, Phenom 

Video Directed and Produced by Visuals by JD.

Haath Varthi Lyrics - 

Mere gaano pe haath varthi,
Agar nahi kiya yaha pe toh maar padhti,
Teri behen mujhse pyaar karti,
Mat maar usko uski nahi galti,
Sirf relate wo karti ,
P town bole toh yede log ki Bharti,
Mai gardish mai Bharti,
Aawaz thodi alag aari hogayeli sardi,
P Town se B Town tak apli chalti !!!

Tum gardi mai chalte toh dikhte nahi ,
Mai gardi mai chalta toh dikhta,
Tu dus time sochenga ,
aisa kyu likhta kyu ki mai sick tha ,
Ayee sickness bana mera dopeness. 
Skateboard Air 1 tight istari,
Kidd mai full homeless boneless staircase, 
Mujh pe kyu chodh dala beat ko ,
Maine chod dala beat ko,
Karu Kya disco MS Stan means, 
Toh darta nahi kisko aayi zavuntak Mitra mandal you know what I’m saying..

Kaisa hua meko pyaar, 
mera homie bola maar, 
Tune jhoot bola kyu ,
Maine diya tera saath!!! 

Mere gaano pe haath varthi ,
Agar nahi kiya yaha pe toh maar padhti,
Teri behen mujhse pyaar karti ,
Mat maar usko uski nahi galti,
Sirf relate wo karti ,
P town bole toh yede log ki Bharti ,
Mai gardish mai Bharti,
Aawaz thodi alag aari hogayeli sardi,
P Town se B Town tak apli chalti !!!

Mai ghusta jab club mai ,
basti ki public aayeli ,
matlab Confirm hai raade,
 It was my worst day  ,
Meri gang mei se koi toh bhi koyta nikale,
Public mai matter bada re ,
Shawty hot dikhri toh chadar failare ,
Yeh mere pe trapa bithare ,
Maa baap ko bolre haan Inlog ne maare,
Club mai teko entry nahi ,
Guest list mai naam tera maam hamne badach ka dale ,
Yeh Meko lagte bichare ,
Meri galti Kya inlog ke numbers nahi aare ,
Yeh Meko taadi pilare , yeh bache log Meko kyu taadi pilare ,
Daru mat paani pila re ,
Party mai entry hui toh shawty chupare.. !!

Mere gaano pe haath varthi ,
Agar nahi kiya yaha pe toh maar padhti,
Teri behen mujhse pyaar karti ,
Mat maar usko uski nahi galti,
Sirf relate wo karti ,
P town bole toh yede log ki Bharti, 
Mai gardish mai Bharti ,
Aawaz thodi alag aari hogayeli sardi ,
P Town se B Town tak apli chalti!!!

Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. Vinu Kaka would be visiting their home for Popatlal, so Madhavi and Bhide prepare all the particular arrangements for him. Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: NEW! Dhruv Tara - Samay Sadi Se Pare  - EP 70 - 18 May 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 70: Doctor Dhurv Ki Jai
---------------------------------------------------------
The King of Vallabhgarh Tara's father orders the attendants to release Doctor Dhruv to treat her daughter. Dhruv finally saves Tara's life, and the people of Vallabhgarh praise Doctor Dhruv's skill. Tara gradually gains consciousness and shows her gratitude to him. Sukanya gets praised by Princess Tara Priya too. Dhruv is finally taken to Mahaveer's room for his treatment by Tara. Later, Jai, Aisha's husband, finds divorce papers in his closet, which startles him. Stay tuned to learn more!

Show Name – Dhruv Tara - Samay Sadi Se Pare
Star Cast –  Riya Sharma, Ishaan Dhawan, Yash Tonk, Swati Kapoor, Krishna Bharadwaj
Episodes No - 70, 18 May 2023
Produced By - Sumeet Mittal and Shashi Mittal

#Dhruvtara  #dhruvtarasamaysadisepare  #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About the show : 
---------------------------------------------------------------------
Dhruv Tara Samay Sadi Se Pare is an Indian Romantic Drama on Sab. Dhruv and Tara, who come from various eras, are at the center of the narrative. A 17th-century princess named Tara travels across time and finds herself in the present, where she meets Dhruv. Tara has arrived in the twenty-first century in search of treatment for her brother's illness. When an unidentified "dupatta" from the 17th century falls on Dhruv, he is at the Taj Mahal in Agra. Watch this show to see how a young relationship develops between two people from different times.
